sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Orch as Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Chunker as Caikit Chunker<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Detector as Detector Services<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant GenTGIS as TGIS / Caikit NLP<br/>8033-8085/TCP gRPC
    participant OpenAI as OpenAI / vLLM<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant OTLP as OTLP Collector<br/>4317/TCP

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 1: Classification with Text Generation (v1 API)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v1/task/classification-with-text-generation<br/>Optional TLS, Header passthrough
    Orch->>Chunker: Chunk input text<br/>gRPC, Optional TLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text segments
    Orch->>Detector: Input detection (parallel per detector)<br/>POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Optional TLS, Optional Bearer
    Detector-->>Orch: Input detection results
    Orch->>GenTGIS: Generate text<br/>gRPC GenerationService/NlpService<br/>Optional TLS
    GenTGIS-->>Orch: Generated text
    Orch->>Detector: Output detection (parallel per detector)<br/>POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Optional TLS, Optional Bearer
    Detector-->>Orch: Output detection results
    Orch-->>Client: JSON response with generation + detections

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 2: OpenAI Chat Completions with Detection (v2 API)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Optional TLS, Header passthrough
    Orch->>Detector: Input detection on last message<br/>POST /api/v1/text/chat<br/>Optional Bearer
    Detector-->>Orch: Input detection results
    Orch->>OpenAI: POST /v1/chat/completions (streaming or unary)<br/>Optional TLS, Optional Bearer
    OpenAI-->>Orch: SSE stream or JSON response
    Orch->>Chunker: Chunk output text<br/>gRPC, Optional TLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked segments
    Orch->>Detector: Output detection (parallel per detector)<br/>Optional Bearer
    Detector-->>Orch: Output detection results
    Orch-->>Client: SSE stream or JSON with detections

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 3: Streaming Content Detection (v2 API)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/stream-content<br/>ND-JSON stream, Optional TLS
    Orch->>Chunker: Bidirectional streaming chunking<br/>gRPC BidiStreamingChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked segments (streaming)
    Orch->>Detector: Concurrent batched detection<br/>POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Optional Bearer
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results (batched)
    Orch-->>Client: ND-JSON stream with detection results

    Note over Orch,OTLP: Telemetry (all flows)
    Orch->>OTLP: Export traces and metrics<br/>gRPC/HTTP, Plaintext
